## Read Todos

### All todos
GET http://localhost:3000/todos

### Specific todo
GET http://localhost:3000/todos/YOUR_TODO_ID

### Completed todos
GET http://localhost:3000/todos/completed

### Pending todos
GET http://localhost:3000/todos/pending

### By priority - High
GET http://localhost:3000/todos/priority/high

### By priority - Medium
GET http://localhost:3000/todos/priority/medium

### By priority - Low
GET http://localhost:3000/todos/priority/low

## Search

### Search todos
GET http://localhost:3000/todos/search?q=milk

###
GET http://localhost:3000/todos/search?q=house

## Update Todos

### Update todo
PUT http://localhost:3000/todos/YOUR_TODO_ID
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Buy milk and bread",
  "completed": true
}

### Toggle status
PATCH http://localhost:3000/todos/YOUR_TODO_ID/toggle

## Delete Todos

### Delete specific todo
DELETE http://localhost:3000/todos/YOUR_TODO_ID

### Delete all completed todos
DELETE http://localhost:3000/todos

## Statistics

### General statistics
GET http://localhost:3000/todos/stats

